image_analysis.description: A street-level photograph taken in New York City. The image shows the corner of Madison Avenue and East 71st Street. On the left is a Ralph Lauren storefront with a blue awning. In the center, street signs indicate 'Madison Av' and 'E 71 St' along with 'ONE WAY' signs. In the background, a brownstone building with gothic-style windows (likely a church) is visible. On the right, a yellow and blue Sabrett hot dog stand umbrella is prominent. A white USPS delivery truck is partially visible in the background with the text 'We Deliver For You' and 'www.usps.com'.
